Package fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.declarative.previewers

Interface Previewer<T extends PatternInterface>

Type Parameters:
T - The type of pattern returned by the run runPreview(float, int)} method.
All Known Implementing Classes:
ARMPreviewer, IMPreviewer
public interface Previewer<T extends PatternInterface>
Allows to return a defined number of solutions to get a preview of the request.

  • Method Details

    • differentRequest

      static boolean differentRequest(AbstractChocoMiningExperience chocoMiningExperience)
      Checks whether the current instance of the PreviewerCurrentExperience.chocoMiningExperience is different from the one used in the new request.
      Parameters:
      chocoMiningExperience - the experience created by the new request.
      Returns:
      true if the current instance of the PreviewerCurrentExperience.chocoMiningExperience is different from the experience created by the new request.
      See Also:
      • AbstractChocoMiningExperience

    • runPreview

      Solutions<T> runPreview(float timeout, int maxSol)
      Runs the preview It either returns :
      - A number of solutions lower or equals to the maxSol threshold defined.
      - The solutions found until the runtime of the method surpassed the timeout defined.
      - The solutions found until there were no more solutions found by the solver (PreviewerCurrentExperience.currentSolver).
      Parameters:
      timeout - the maximum runtime of the method.
      maxSol - the maximum allowed number of solutions to be returned.
      Returns:
      the solved and parsed solutions.
